117
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:32,700
Yao, you...

118
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,540
♪Drifting back through the snow♪

119
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:40,300
I don't blame you.

120
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:41,940
It's not your fault.

121
