164
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:03,380
Because of my mother.

165
00:10:04,220 --> 00:10:05,060
Your mother?

166
00:10:07,650 --> 00:10:08,580
My mother had a gentle nature.

167
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,700
Whenever she was upset,

168
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,500
