169
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,940
Later, she took me with her.

170
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,500
Skip stones?

171
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:18,900
But I remember

172
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:20,300
you always just threw stones

173
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:21,580
into the river.

174
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,380
Because I couldn't do it right.

175
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:25,860
I could never get the strength right.

176
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,420
My mother would laugh at me

177
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:28,660
