180
00:10:34,260 --> 00:10:35,860
to make your mother happy.

181
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:53,260
These years,

182
00:10:54,010 --> 00:10:55,900
I've been searching for Master's body

183
00:10:57,180 --> 00:10:58,860
and looking for you.

184
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,380
